description: Just so that we can all come back down to earth and don't forget that not all women are over-achievers like Jade Marxx or Veronika, today we're giving you Jessica. She obviously liked the Monster, I'm not so sure about the other machines. Don't worry, I won't leave you out to dry, this will be an interim update, this Friday I will either add the eternal Venus, or a smoking hot new girl, Lucy Lee.
title: Jessica Sexin
